## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of studies reviewed. While the sources provide a comprehensive overview, there may be additional factors and nuances not covered in this summary. Furthermore, the impact of redlining can vary significantly across different regions and communities, which may not be fully captured in the selected studies. Future research could benefit from more localized studies and longitudinal data to better understand the evolving impact of redlining.